attributes.title: I can’t read anything
attributes.review: I tried finding Pig Latin in the language settings but as far as I could see it only has English as an option. I was trying to read it while roller blading down a street and got so confused that I crashed into a stop sign that had graffiti on it. The graffiti read « [STOP] Biden 2020. » I then realized that this incident was not only a physical sign but also a metaphorical one. Then a bird pooped on my head. Good luck, I guess. Because of your lack of language options, I am now tired, injured, smell like poop, and am voting for Biden.
